Command to build docker image:

docker build -t "ytmonitor:latest" .

Command to start docker image (Chromium is picky and requires "priveleges"):

docker run -it --privileged ytmonitor:1.0.0 /home/ytmonitor/start-monitor

Command to remove "dangling" images:

docker rmi -f $(docker images -f "dangling=true" -q)

Commands to stop auto-restart containers:

docker update --restart=no $(docker ps -a -q)

Usage of --restart=unless-stopped is recommended.

